<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="arial">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>You recently made a request to amend your policy.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><b>Our Underwriting Team need additional information from you in order to process this request</b></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> so we would be grateful if you can provide answers to the questions below.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Please </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">return your answers at your earliest convenience</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> and we will aim to respond with a decision as soon as possible. Please be as thorough as possible in your response, as this will help speed up the checking process.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><i>(add any questions here)<br></i></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><i><br></i>If you have any questions or queries please get in touch on </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">01242 808 740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
